OL,4,Ccharge of riot
OL,6,FRiot carries a maximum sentence of 10
OL,7,Fyears and is a more serious charge
OL,8,Fthan violent disorder, which most
OL,9,Fother defendants from the recent
OL,10,Fnationwide trouble have faced.
OL,12,FViolent disorder suspects across the
OL,13,Fcountry await news on whether they
OL,14,Fwill be accused of the more serious
OL,15,Foffence.
OL,17,FChristopher Atkinson, Head of the
OL,18,FComplex Casework Unit for CPS North
OL,19,FEast, said: "Kieran Usher played a
OL,20,Fpivotal role in the events that last
OL,21,Fmonth blighted the city of Sunderland.
