OL,4,Ccharge of riot
OL,6,F"The significant sentence that he now
OL,7,Ffaces appropriately reflects the
OL,8,Fseverity of his actions, which saw him
OL,9,Fco-ordinate with at least twenty other
OL,10,Fpeople to rain missiles onto attending
OL,11,Fpolice officers in the course of their
OL,12,Fduties to protect the public.
OL,14,F"Despite the aggression they faced
OL,15,Fthat evening, Northumbria Police have
OL,16,Fprovided us with hours of evidential
OL,17,Fmaterial. This has been instrumental
OL,18,Fin identifying those responsible for
OL,19,Fthese shameful events, enabling us to
OL,20,Fclearly illustrate to the courts the
OL,21,Fspecific role that each person played.
