OL,6,F"The Crown Prosecution Service will
OL,7,Fcontinue to work alongside our
OL,8,Fcriminal justice partners to ensure
OL,9,Fthat anyone threatening the
OL,10,Fcommunities we serve are swiftly
OL,11,Fbrought to justice for their actions."
OL,13,FDisorder was sparked across the
OL,14,Fcountry following the fatal stabbing
OL,15,Fof three young girls in Southport,
OL,16,Fafter it was falsely claimed online
OL,17,Fthe perpetrator was an illegal
OL,18,Fimmigrant.
